00:48:11.190 --> 00:48:14.450
survive if it goes to 30,
and thrive if it goes to 70.

00:48:14.450 --> 00:48:16.920
But it's another thing
to say oil is 50,

00:48:16.920 --> 00:48:18.772
I think it's going
